Just from my observation I notice that after I walked into the  establishment a Caucasian couple was greeted with warmth and politeness of customers service . After Nal finished  my sandwich , two African Americans walked into the establishment and were not greeted with the same warm welcoming. Nal continued to cash me out with repulsion of disgust  as if he wanted me to leave immediately(Droped my receipt out of hand /walked away). I’ve experienced  this transaction with him prior but never said anything due to people having bad days in this industry.But my observation alone was enough to say this is ENOUGH . Everyone should be treated with the same regardless of race or ethical backgrounds.

I thoroughly enjoyed my build-your-own veggie salad w/a side of tuna! Waaay healthier than their heavily breaded paninis... which, don't get me wrong, looked delicious!!! Just too much bread especially if u see the size of the bread b4 it's smashed down in the press.  That aside, u can eat healthy @fast food establishments! 🙌🏽 I chose 2 get a couple slices of bread on the side of my salad. Still delish! Fewer carbs that turn 2 sugar! Plus dressing ON THE SIDE!!! Dip my fork in b4 picking up salad & still get flavor minus all the calories & fat!  Very roomy restaurant w/standard table & chairs, window barstool & outdoor patio seating!  Beautiful selection of veggies, nuts & a variety of meats. But vegetarian & vegans have a nice selection of whole-food, plant-based options!!! Yay!
